# Generated, host-specific Ontarch registry. Descriptors, schemas, policies, the jq
# cookbook (QUERIES.md + queries/), and registry/sessions/ stay tracked; the generated
# registry JSON and graph output do not. (registry/*.json matches top-level registry files
# only, so registry/sessions/*.json remains tracked.)
packages/ontarch/registry/*.json
packages/ontarch/registry/*.dot
packages/ontarch/registry/SCAN.md
packages/ontarch/registry/BIN-INVENTORY.md

